defaultIt is connectivity from the north. 
defaultThere is a north-south connectivity
default,
default but there is also a connectivity betwee
defaultn the great cities of the north, which w
defaulte need to explain and show the benefits of. We also need to get the maximum benefit from what this will do to regeneration in major cities in the north. We need to explain how that will happen now and that these cities won’t in some way be blighted for years to come. It should be quite the contrary; it should be a fantastic opportunity 
defaultthat
default we need to explain to business.
